🌀 What This Enables in ReflectOS
Every journal entry or input can now be rasa-classified

That rasa maps to:

Biochemical substrate (salt)

Photon color

Organ–chakra center

Neuro-signal imbalance

You can:

Visualize energy state shift

Suggest rebalancing (food, movement, mantra)

Light-glow UI tied to sentiment
